(559, 1, 47, 'Get to Know Everything About Using a Multimeter With This Guide', 'http://lifehacker.com/get-to-know-everything-about-using-a-multimeter-with-th-1791173124', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/s--21L5IIT_--/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/ykxzwrtj0gpsvmhc9vxi.jpg', 'Multimeters seem simple enough to use. You turn it on, connect the leads, then start poking things. Really though, there’s a quite a bit going on in a multimeter and a lot of different settings to get used to. Make has a guide that walks you through everything you need to know.', 0, NULL, NULL, 1),
(560, 1, 41, 'Classical Music Mashup II: 52 classical pieces from 31 composers | The Kid Should See This', 'http://thekidshouldseethis.com/post/classical-music-mashup-ii-52-classical-pieces-from-31-composers', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'http://thekidshouldseethis.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/classical-music-mashup-ii-1024x576.jpg', 'Tchaikovsky , Mozart , Verdi , Mendelssohn , Bach , Grieg , and many more composers&#8217; little heads can be seen in this Classical Music Mashup II by Grant Woolard, a follow up to his previous Classical Music Mashup .', 0, NULL, NULL, 1),
(561, 1, 31, 'A visual history of gadgets that have burst into flames', 'https://www.engadget.com/2017/01/15/gadgets-that-have-burst-into-flames-or-exploded/', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://s.aolcdn.com/dims-shared/dims3/GLOB/crop/5064x3328%2B0%2B0/resize/1600x1052%21/format/jpg/quality/85/https://s.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/2238a7da01d21198a0d6bdf99313b6a3/204460616/RTSR0T5.jpeg', 'Samsung had a rough 2016 . Last year, the company had to recall its Galaxy Note 7 after units were catching fire, followed by millions of washing machines that were exploding in people\'s homes. But Samsung isn\'t the only company that\'s struggled recently with faulty batteries. We\'ve seen similar issues with hoverboards, a Tesla Model S and the latest electric skateboard from Boosted. Let\'s take a look at other products that have had trouble in the flammability department. And let\'s hope those non-exploding lithium Ion batteries get here soon.', 0, NULL, NULL, 1),
(562, 1, 47, 'Top 10 Raspberry Pi Projects for Beginners', 'http://lifehacker.com/top-10-raspberry-pi-projects-for-beginners-1791002723', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/s--Cp4KCWm6--/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/p377mdnv1ujlspfboj7b.png', 'Maybe you picked up a Raspberry Pi for the holidays, or you’ve been sitting on one of the super versatile, palm-sized computers for a while now. If you’ve been wondering how to get started with yours , or what you could build that’s worthwhile, here are ten great ideas.', 0, NULL, NULL, 1),
(563, 1, 35, 'Kosovo&#039;s First Pi Wars - Raspberry Pi', 'https://www.raspberrypi.org/blog/kosovos-first-pi-wars/', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://www.raspberrypi.org/app/uploads/2016/11/2016-10-18-11.10.42.jpg', 'British engineer Andy Moxon recently contacted us to highlight a Pi Wars event he was organising in Kosovo.', 0, NULL, NULL, 1),
